    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>A PRISON FOR MAURICE RIVER</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Andrew Jacobs</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Jacobs, Andrew</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Officials in Maurice River, NJ, agree to accept prison that would house 300 sexually violent predators (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Officials in Maurice River, a rural community on the Delaware Bay, agreed to accept a prison that would house 300 ''sexually violent predators.'' Woodbridge officials had been fighting the plans to build the facility there. Maurice River, already home to two medium-security prisons, will receive $825,000 from the state when the facility opens, and $200,000 a year while it is being built.</p>
        <p>Andrew Jacobs</p>
      </block>
